text: San Carlos is a corregimiento in David District, Chiriquí Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 4,487 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 2,543; its population as of 2000 was 3,181. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Chiriquí Province
